title: ENOi
text:
ENOi (Korean: 이엔오아이) was a seven member South Korean boy band formed by KiTheWhale in 2019. The group debuted on April 19, 2019, with "Bloom". They disbanded on January 22, 2021.


== Former members ==
Laon (라온) - leader, vocalist
Dojin (도진) - rapper
Hamin (하민) - vocalist
Avin (어빈) - vocalist
Jinwoo (진우) - vocalist
J-kid (제이키드) - vocalist
Gun (건) - rapper
